<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><i style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br>(Use for those who notified us)<br></font></i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">I hope you don’t mind me contacting you regarding your potential <i>(insert claim type)</i> and our email sent on <i>(insert date)</i>.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please could you let me know if you wish to make a claim and do let me know if you require any assistance in collecting the information requested in order that we may present a claim.<br></span><i style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>(Use for those where we received notification)<br></i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">We have received notification from another party looking to claim against you. Please could you provide the details requested as your policy with us may be able to respond.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please note insurers are not yet aware of your claim until you forward the details below in order for me to present.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br><i>(For PI do not reference to still wishing to make a claim as all PI claims need referring to insurers.)<br></i></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Claims Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: claims@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>